Uptime Kuma is a self-hosted monitoring tool with a clean, modern interface. Monitor your websites, APIs, and services using HTTP(s), TCP, Ping, DNS, Docker, MQTT, WebSocket, gRPC, and more. Get instant alerts through 87+ notification providers including Telegram, Discord, Slack, and Email. Create beautiful public status pages, track SSL certificate expiry, view response time graphs and uptime statistics. Supports 2FA authentication, proxy configurations, and maintenance windows.